POE-Component-IRC-Plugin-Infobot version 0.001003
=================================================

POE::Component::IRC::Plugin::Infobot is a PoCo-IRC plugin that makes
a PoCo-IRC behave like a simple infobot.

It stores factoids in a DB_File database and lets IRC users add, remove
and retreive factoids.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

* IRC::Utils
* POE::Component::IRC

